"content": "<style>\nh1.thlex-title { font-size: 1.3em; margin: 0 0 0.4em; }\n.thlex-key { color: #888; font-size: 0.85em; font-weight: normal; margin-right: 0.4em; }\nnav.thlex-index { margin: 0.5em 0 0.75em; }\nnav.thlex-index ul { margin: 0; padding-left: 1.2em; }\nnav.thlex-index li { margin: 0.15em 0; font-size: 0.95em; }\n.thlex-section { margin: 0.6em 0; }\nh2.thlex-heading { font-size: 1em; margin: 0.5em 0 0.2em; }\nh3.thlex-subheading { font-size: 0.95em; font-weight: normal; font-style: italic; margin: 0.2em 0; }\n.thlex-language-sets { margin: 0.3em 0 0.3em 1em; }\n.thlex-language-set { margin: 0.4em 0; padding-left: 0.75em; border-left: 3px solid #e0e0e0; }\n.thlex-language { font-size: 0.8em; color: #888; margin-right: 0.4em; }\n.thlex-lemma { font-weight: bold; font-family: serif; }\n.thlex-translit { color: #555; font-style: italic; font-size: 0.9em; margin-left: 0.3em; }\n.thlex-refs { font-size: 0.85em; color: #444; margin-top: 0.15em; }\n.thlex-paragraphs p { margin: 0.35em 0; font-size: 0.95em; line-height: 1.5; }\n.thlex-image { margin: 0.5em 0; display: block; }\n.thlex-image img { max-width: 100%; height: auto; display: block; }\nfigcaption.thlex-caption { font-size: 0.85em; color: #555; font-style: italic; margin-top: 0.2em; }\n.thlex-abbr { border-bottom: 1px dotted #888; cursor: help; }\n.thlex-xref { color: #1a5fb4; }\nspan[data-bnType=\"bibleReference\"] { color: #1a5fb4; }\ntable.thlex-table { border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 0.9em; margin: 0.5em 0; }\ntable.thlex-table td { padding: 0.2em 0.6em; vertical-align: top; border: 1px solid #ddd; }\ntable.thlex-table tr:first-child td { font-weight: bold; background: #f5f5f5; }\nul.thlex-index-list { margin: 0.4em 0; padding-left: 1.4em; font-size: 0.95em; line-height: 1.6; }\nul.thlex-index-list ul { margin: 0.1em 0; padding-left: 1.4em; }\n.thlex-index-key { font-weight: bold; font-style: italic; }\n</style><h1 class=\"thlex-title\" id=\"REALIA:4.6.6\"><span class=\"thlex-key\">4.6.6</span> 标题：圣柱、圣石、纪念石（sacred pillar, sacred stone, memorial stone）</h1><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">经文出处</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-sets\">\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">来：מַצֵּבָה, מַצֶּבֶת</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：matsevah, matseveth)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen28:18\">GEN 28:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen28:22\">GEN 28:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen31:13\">GEN 31:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen31:45\">GEN 31:45</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen31:51\">GEN 31:51</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen31:52\">GEN 31:52</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen31:52\">GEN 31:52</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen35:14\">GEN 35:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen35:14\">GEN 35:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen35:20\">GEN 35:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen35:20\">GEN 35:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod23:24\">EXO 23:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod24:4\">EXO 24:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod34:13\">EXO 34:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev26:1\">LEV 26:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut7:5\">DEU 7:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut12:3\">DEU 12:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut16:22\">DEU 16:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam18:18\">2SA 18:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam18:18\">2SA 18:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs14:23\">1KI 14:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs3:2\">2KI 3:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs10:26\">2KI 10:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs10:27\">2KI 10:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs17:10\">2KI 17:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs18:4\">2KI 18:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs23:14\">2KI 23:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr14:2\">2CH 14:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr31:1\">2CH 31:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa19:19\">ISA 19:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer43:13\">JER 43:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek26:11\">EZK 26:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos3:4\">HOS 3:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos10:1\">HOS 10:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos10:2\">HOS 10:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic5:12\">MIC 5:12</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希：στήλη</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：stēlē)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Macc14:26\">1MA 14:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/3Macc2:27\">3MA 2:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/3Macc7:20\">3MA 7:20</a></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">描述</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>\n            <figure class=\"thlex-image\"><img class=\"thlex-img\" src=\"images/WEB-0465_pillar_memorial_stone.jpg\" alt=\"神圣的柱子\"><figcaption class=\"thlex-caption\">神圣的柱子 (Gary Todd, Israel Museum, CC0, via Wikimedia Commons)</figcaption></figure>圣柱是一根柱子，通常由一整块石头做成，上面有时会刻着铭文，纪念石头竖立的地方发生的某个事件。这样的纪念碑可以是一块大石头或一堆石头。</p>\n<hr/>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">翻译</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>在圣经文化中，为特殊的神圣目的竖立碑石是常见的做法。立碑是为了纪念重要的事件，例如神明显灵或军事胜利，或者表示庄严地起誓或立约，或者永久纪念某位祖先或其他名人。</p>\n<p>希伯来文<em>matsevah</em> 和<em>matseveth</em> 用来表示两种不同的事物。一方面，这两个词都可以表示符合律法的立碑行为，甚至是为上帝而立，如<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa19:19\">ISA 19:19</a> 所述的情况。另一方面，这种纪念石也可能是拜偶像的人为尊崇他们的神明所立的。后一种情况受到圣经强烈的谴责，圣经甚至吩咐以色列人要打碎他们的柱像（如<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod23:24\">EXO 23:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut7:5\">DEU 7:5</a> ）。有些语言会用不同的词语或修饰语来区分这两者；例如，在<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen35:14\">GEN 35:14</a> ，<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Good News Translation (1992)\">GNT</abbr> 将希伯来文<em>matsevah</em> 译为“memorial stone”（“纪念石”），而在<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod23:24\">EXO 23:24</a> ，同一个词被译为“sacred stone pillars”（“神圣的石柱”）。有些翻译者会用描述性的短语对“纪念石”进行扩展翻译，如“很大的石头，好叫他记住那里曾经发生的事情”（<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Contemporary English Version\">CEV</abbr> 直译）。</p>\n<p>纪念石（通常被称为见证）出现在<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen28:18\">GEN 28:18</a> ，<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen28:22\">GEN 28:22</a> ，<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen31:13\">GEN 31:13</a> ，<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen31:45\">GEN 31:45</a> ，<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen31:51\">GEN 31:51</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen31:52\">GEN 31:52</a> ，<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen35:14\">GEN 35:14</a> ，<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen35:20\">GEN 35:20</a> ；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod24:4\">EXO 24:4</a> ；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam18:18\">2SA 18:18</a> ；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa19:19\">ISA 19:19</a> 。</p>\n<p>圣石出现在<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod23:24\">EXO 23:24</a> ，<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod34:13\">EXO 34:13</a> ；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev26:1\">LEV 26:1</a> ；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut7:5\">DEU 7:5</a> ，<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut12:3\">DEU 12:3</a> ，<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut16:22\">DEU 16:22</a> ；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs14:23\">1KI 14:23</a> ；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs3:2\">2KI 3:2</a> ，<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs10:26\">2KI 10:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs10:27\">2KI 10:27</a> ，<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs17:10\">2KI 17:10</a> ，<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs18:4\">2KI 18:4</a> ，<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs23:14\">2KI 23:14</a> ；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr14:2\">2CH 14:2</a> （《和》14:3），<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr31:1\">2CH 31:1</a> ；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer43:13\">JER 43:13</a> ；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek26:11\">EZK 26:11</a> ；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos3:4\">HOS 3:4</a> ，<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos10:1\">HOS 10:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos10:2\">HOS 10:2</a> ；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic5:12\">MIC 5:12</a> （《和》5:13）。</p>\n</div>\n</div>",
